<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>詩詞 on Script Adults</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/categories/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/</link><description>Recent content in 詩詞 on Script Adults</description><image><title>Script Adults</title><url>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</url><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</link></image><generator>Hugo -- 0.140.0</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 19:19:22 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://katsuragicsl.github.io/categories/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>幼貧而樂今殷而戚問何所為也</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%B9%BC%E8%B2%A7%E8%80%8C%E6%A8%82%E4%BB%8A%E6%AE%B7%E8%80%8C%E6%88%9A%E5%95%8F%E4%BD%95%E6%89%80%E7%82%BA%E4%B9%9F/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 19:19:22 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%B9%BC%E8%B2%A7%E8%80%8C%E6%A8%82%E4%BB%8A%E6%AE%B7%E8%80%8C%E6%88%9A%E5%95%8F%E4%BD%95%E6%89%80%E7%82%BA%E4%B9%9F/</guid><description>&lt;p>坐立皆不適，忡忡何所憂？&lt;br>
居毋患寒暑，食盡啖珍饈。&lt;br>
幼自貧窮慣，今唯前咎愁。&lt;br>
何如曲肱枕，淡飯敢焚裘。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>隱學典難覓</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%9A%B1%E5%AD%B8%E5%85%B8%E9%9B%A3%E8%A6%93/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 18:49:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%9A%B1%E5%AD%B8%E5%85%B8%E9%9B%A3%E8%A6%93/</guid><description>&lt;p>情鍾隱學典難覓，眼澀抬頭日已斜。&lt;br>
古籍奇書尚能借，春秋有數問誰賒。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>自樂</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%87%AA%E6%A8%82/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 02:54:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%87%AA%E6%A8%82/</guid><description>&lt;p>懶理職場獻媚密，歸來自聽雨連珠。&lt;br>
凡生笑我無心眼，漆吏知吾乃樂魚。&lt;br>
孔聖隨心不踰矩，詩痴久諷律無虞。&lt;br>
唯耽無益雕蟲技，最是優悠意氣舒。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>文采狂</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%96%87%E9%87%87%E7%8B%82/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 21:53:52 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%96%87%E9%87%87%E7%8B%82/</guid><description>&lt;p>分明昨日痾甚篤，費解今宵文采狂。&lt;br>
病體疑為煉丹鼎，丹成病好筆生光。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>論文化侵蝕</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%AB%96%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%BE%B5%E8%9D%95/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 21:52:41 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%AB%96%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%BE%B5%E8%9D%95/</guid><description>&lt;p>近世多鵲壘，鳲鳩豐尾垂。&lt;br>
鳲鳩施小利，鵲語改相隨。&lt;br>
客佔雖多地，東家尚有墟。&lt;br>
毋蹈楚王轍，魯莽贈烏騅。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>不寐又思早起</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%90%E5%8F%88%E6%80%9D%E6%97%A9%E8%B5%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 21:45:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%90%E5%8F%88%E6%80%9D%E6%97%A9%E8%B5%B7/</guid><description>&lt;p>寅時初夏雨，淅瀝擾休眠。&lt;br>
冷氣頭上響，炎風廳裡燃。&lt;br>
閒姑倚書案，久若坐針氈。&lt;br>
旦日還待呷，齋啡微苦漣。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>憶杯渡</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E6%9D%AF%E6%B8%A1/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 02:32:32 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E6%9D%AF%E6%B8%A1/</guid><description>&lt;p>童年夏必逢飛蟻，舍妹心驚急淚潺。&lt;br>
晚煮杯茶憶杯渡，青絲初白夢青山。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>贈妻一絕</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%B4%88%E5%A6%BB%E4%B8%80%E7%B5%95/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 02:31:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%B4%88%E5%A6%BB%E4%B8%80%E7%B5%95/</guid><description>&lt;p>昏燈暖透夜閨房，細看床前換寢裝。&lt;br>
枉詡能詩多健筆，無言倚枕醉幽芳。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>問道</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%95%8F%E9%81%93/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 02:30:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%95%8F%E9%81%93/</guid><description>&lt;p>行年三十一，佇路覓繩韁。&lt;br>
問道莊周樹，尋花蝶夢鄉。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>職場自嘲</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 02:05:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2/</guid><description>&lt;p>力壯常揮劍，堂堂六呎夫。&lt;br>
惶惶乞升斗，瘁死有餘辜。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>鑽石山母親節聚餐</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%B1%B1%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80%E8%81%9A%E9%A4%90/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 18:56:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%B1%B1%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80%E8%81%9A%E9%A4%90/</guid><description>&lt;p>蓮園喜無雨，好節聚茶几。&lt;br>
醉焗竹蟶嫩，香煎露筍肥。&lt;br>
親應少時養，食慾老來微。&lt;br>
尚慰纖纖箸，頻頻碟上飛。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>易主</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%93%E4%B8%BB/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 15:01:26 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%93%E4%B8%BB/</guid><description>&lt;p>老號金主易，才賢歸梓桑。&lt;br>
坊中無事瑣，役婦手機忙。&lt;br>
既屢裁員狠，還期仕氣昂？&lt;br>
時衰沐猴冠，豎子坐高堂。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>憶中大</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 03:01:02 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7/</guid><description>&lt;p>夢入當年新亞宿，涼乘合一水旁陰。&lt;br>
青山一別書香薄，石壁空鐫名姓深。&lt;br>
錯把孤居作勤學，徒懷熱鬧論經音。&lt;br>
盈頭鬒髮今朝落，默撫長鬚復擁衾。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>詠巴西柔術</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%9F%94%E8%A1%93/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 03:00:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%9F%94%E8%A1%93/</guid><description>&lt;p>褒衣博帶非儒服，肉搏毫釐不動刀。&lt;br>
灑汗披襟相浹背，騎胸抱頸若分桃。&lt;br>
難如對奕能開智，巧使剛柔解六韜。&lt;br>
此藝修心養吾性，藏鋒斂戾伏波濤。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>喜見群友良緣</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%96%9C%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%A4%E5%8F%8B%E8%89%AF%E7%B7%A3/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 02:58:09 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%96%9C%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%A4%E5%8F%8B%E8%89%AF%E7%B7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p>喜見同群締佳偶，如聞弄玉鳳凰簫。&lt;br>
誰云嗜語招人異，得遇才媛桃自夭。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>歸人</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%AD%B8%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 02:57:49 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%AD%B8%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>&lt;p>滾滾車連轂，歸人溢路邊。&lt;br>
霓虹遮月影，路樹攝塵煙。&lt;br>
俗務何竭慮，三旬無撫弦。&lt;br>
樓高山不語，夜靜反無眠。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>大涌橋路</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B6%8C%E6%A9%8B%E8%B7%AF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:06:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B6%8C%E6%A9%8B%E8%B7%AF/</guid><description>&lt;p>向晚歸車涌上過，遺田古早有牛鞅。 &lt;br>
朝擠港島珠纓路，夜食沙田布袋糧。 &lt;br>
幾覆瀝青橋主易，唯留兩岸水湄長。 &lt;br>
幽村狗喚誰家鬼，一叫三迴促斷腸。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>閱杜甫生平</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%B1%E6%9D%9C%E7%94%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B3/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:05:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%B1%E6%9D%9C%E7%94%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B3/</guid><description>&lt;p>嘗題蜀相三分國，又寄宮垣想玉珂。&lt;br>
久憶洛都疲慧眼，心傷楚地殞冬河。&lt;br>
憂民睿敏蟬聯出，不變江山又幾多。&lt;br>
宋滅元亡明復繼，何需俊傑枉蹉跎。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>望華街</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:04:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97/</guid><description>&lt;p>日出華街盈客旅，深宵穢巷舞蠅蚊。&lt;br>
光陰不惜花齡女，玉手磨成半片皸。&lt;br>
昨夢金貂英氣煥，明朝滿鏡老眉矄。&lt;br>
三坪礎剷千年樹，百載勞來兩尺墳。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Work from home</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/work-from-home/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 01:57:02 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/work-from-home/</guid><description>&lt;p>職務能遙理，誰踰廨署埤。&lt;br>
螢屏傳案牘，午灶暖餘糜。&lt;br>
滌釜甘霖躍，臨窗鬧巷熙。&lt;br>
同僚誠喜見，更愛自家籬。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>古不賤今</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A4%E4%BB%8A/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 01:56:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A4%E4%BB%8A/</guid><description>&lt;p>人常詠古歌仁聖，似是今人鄙不勝。&lt;br>
叔夜孤高難仿效，夷齊朽滯若瘕癥。&lt;br>
西山槁槁饑薇蕨，一曲淒淒絕廣陵。&lt;br>
史內千秋寸心辨，賢愚莫有固規繩。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>見族人炫祖上之富</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A6%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%AB%E7%A5%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%AF%8C/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:35:25 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A6%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%AB%E7%A5%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%AF%8C/</guid><description>&lt;p>誰家三水田千里，舊榭新軒盡姓陳。&lt;br>
輒耀膏粱矜祖富，詩書少讀曝詞貧。&lt;br>
詢其祖業餘多少，賞彼紅腮半怯嗔。&lt;br>
渴鬼愁看舊時屋，年年祭饗供他人。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>無題</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 22:33:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</guid><description>&lt;p>陳衣欲搗子規啼，嗽穿重簾夜更淒。&lt;br>
十載茅齋茂陵臥，雙行枯淚太常妻。&lt;br>
清心昔捨青雲路，俗務今催洗耳溪。&lt;br>
半世徒勞芳自賞，來生捨筆執鋤犁。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>憶遊摩周湖</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E9%81%8A%E6%91%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%B9%96/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 02:31:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E9%81%8A%E6%91%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%B9%96/</guid><description>&lt;p>久慕摩周泊，霙遊弟子町。&lt;br>
盤湖青壁峭，漫靄雪濱暝。&lt;br>
水闊連雲影，藍深莫片萍。&lt;br>
天鵝神渚過，幾欲問仙齡。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>漫郎愁</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%BC%AB%E9%83%8E%E6%84%81/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:24:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%BC%AB%E9%83%8E%E6%84%81/</guid><description>&lt;p>平生福禍求諸己，豈冀張良借箸籌。&lt;br>
怨得春時秋亦去，芳時不待漫郎愁。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>拗相公</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%8B%97%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%AC/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:23:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%8B%97%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%AC/</guid><description>&lt;p>煩言少語漠修飾，鐵石心腸拗相公。&lt;br>
滿腹嗔痴熬鬱結，唯題恚賦怨長空。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>春病</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%A5%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:22:34 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%A5%E7%97%85/</guid><description>&lt;p>春衫濕濕雨還淹，爽颯何知昨日炎。&lt;br>
一暖一寒多感冒，鉛頭鉛瞼鐵毫尖。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>宿酒</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%BF%E9%85%92/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:12:05 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%BF%E9%85%92/</guid><description>&lt;p>乃耳春桃赤，方乾竟欲斟。&lt;br>
酣歌忘篋笥，宿酒爛柯尋。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>直鉤詞</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%9B%B4%E9%89%A4%E8%A9%9E/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:10:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%9B%B4%E9%89%A4%E8%A9%9E/</guid><description>&lt;p>嘗聞我氏姜牙祖，百煉參來妙直鉤。&lt;br>
際遇諒如垂澗釣，樵漁宿志待成周。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>望金鐘雨</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E9%9B%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:07:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E9%9B%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p>眺望金鐘雨，禁思海外朋。&lt;br>
聞琴忘荈冷，曲散熄孤燈。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>白梣詠</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%99%BD%E6%A2%A3%E8%A9%A0/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:13:59 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%99%BD%E6%A2%A3%E8%A9%A0/</guid><description>&lt;p>郊車瞥白梣，逸氣惹馳心。&lt;br>
獨直杆齊宇，無憂眾鑠金。&lt;br>
貧泥生色潔，倔質抵風侵。&lt;br>
且倚柴亭樹，朱門少此陰。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>苦戀樹</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8B%A6%E6%88%80%E6%A8%B9/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:02:32 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8B%A6%E6%88%80%E6%A8%B9/</guid><description>&lt;p>苦楝鄉音訛苦戀，人皆笑我若情痴。&lt;br>
情皆巧合亦如此，插柳方成連理枝。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>煙塵望</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%85%99%E5%A1%B5%E6%9C%9B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:00:04 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%85%99%E5%A1%B5%E6%9C%9B/</guid><description>&lt;p>稻謝樓空鳥失巢，矛平戟鏽馬生郊。&lt;br>
髫兒道側尋劬母，怕見霜綾掛樹梢。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>理箱見舊稿</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%90%86%E7%AE%B1%E8%A6%8B%E8%88%8A%E7%A8%BF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 15:58:51 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%90%86%E7%AE%B1%E8%A6%8B%E8%88%8A%E7%A8%BF/</guid><description>&lt;p>嘗來翻舊札，拙作惡難評。&lt;br>
弱歲初經事，繁文欲釣名。&lt;br>
浮詞堆綺句，躁筆抹虛情。&lt;br>
老喜栽詩卉，閒窗細剪莖。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>晚詠</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%99%9A%E8%A9%A0/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 15:57:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%99%9A%E8%A9%A0/</guid><description>&lt;p>山連千樹翠，暉映半川紅。&lt;br>
日暮同歌賦，杯乾意未窮。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>茗汁詞</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8C%97%E6%B1%81%E8%A9%9E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 02:45:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8C%97%E6%B1%81%E8%A9%9E/</guid><description>&lt;p>學淺無他藝，唯長雕琢詞。&lt;br>
沉吟常入定，點卯每來遲。&lt;br>
久病多清興，離群出詭思。&lt;br>
方酣濡墨盡，茗汁代塗之。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>宦海</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%A6%E6%B5%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:06:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%A6%E6%B5%B7/</guid><description>&lt;p>棲身宦海辭難直，隱沒丹心色自萎。&lt;br>
若學嵇公棱角出，便難割肉細君遺。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>閏怨</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%A8%E6%80%A8/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:04:35 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%A8%E6%80%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p>涼風捲髮斷多少，深館籠眉鎖幾重。&lt;br>
縱有沉魚驚世色，夫征不復枉芳容。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>詠志</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%BF%97/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:02:31 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%BF%97/</guid><description>&lt;p>生似離弦箭，宜將鵠志求。&lt;br>
才情師子建，韜略效留侯。&lt;br>
過隧應斬岸，逾河當折舟。&lt;br>
無教箭虛落，白髮泣春秋。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>李恥杜愁</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:01:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</guid><description>&lt;p>性俗全無墨在胸，冥搜拙句砌機峰。&lt;br>
詩成引得謫仙恥，筆落愁催工部容。&lt;br>
既與深情詩韻繫，何教秉賦櫟樗庸。&lt;br>
如吾堪作違心事，簡朽帛殘枯筆封。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>野火</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%87%8E%E7%81%AB/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 21:57:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%87%8E%E7%81%AB/</guid><description>&lt;p>野火吹焦來撲鼻，疑斯處亦啟兵端。&lt;br>
蒼天果有好生德，怎使狼煙剪不完。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>稱病歸沐其二</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%8C/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:23:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%8C/</guid><description>&lt;p>欲借銀鉤掛輕絅，披襟快意抱江潮。&lt;br>
紅塵每每多煩事，擲笏臥花看九霄。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>灣仔商廈觀圬者</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E8%A7%80%E5%9C%AC%E8%80%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:22:35 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E8%A7%80%E5%9C%AC%E8%80%85/</guid><description>&lt;p>久困雕欄內，而無玉砌求。 &lt;br>
無乾圬者汗，盡濕富人樓。 &lt;br>
貴族連三代，貧門到白頭。 &lt;br>
笙歌聽愈擾，喋喋不安休。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>遙寄故人</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%81%99%E5%AF%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:20:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%81%99%E5%AF%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>&lt;p>昨問他鄉花幾許，君稱今日滿山紅。&lt;br>
東風知汝遙憶我，一片吹來孤座中。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>稱病歸沐登獅子山</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E7%99%BB%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B1%B1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:18:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E7%99%BB%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B1%B1/</guid><description>&lt;p>甫陟蒼巔氣清朗，忽憂仕路暗傷神。&lt;br>
何時始得閒如許，莫待衰顏惹滓塵。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>夜讀</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%9C%E8%AE%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:16:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%9C%E8%AE%80/</guid><description>&lt;p>無意尋春色，離群獨筆耕。&lt;br>
風幽星火動，葉蕩夜蟲鳴。&lt;br>
案上半尋闊，心田萬畝宏。&lt;br>
思潮如碧海，引棹到三更。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>不寐</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%90/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 02:21:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%90/</guid><description>&lt;p>夜起喉酸胸似火，窗前恍惚浴寒暉。&lt;br>
素娥招我隨風去，忘卻愁思入繡闈。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>敢擬一詩忖度離鄉客家人愁緒</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%95%A2%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A9%A9%E5%BF%96%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A2%E9%84%89%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%81%E7%B7%92/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 16:11:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%95%A2%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A9%A9%E5%BF%96%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A2%E9%84%89%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%81%E7%B7%92/</guid><description>&lt;p>久滯繁華地，鄉離語更乖。&lt;br>
夢中歸故里，簷下一聲𠊎。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>書癖</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9B%B8%E7%99%96/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 01:11:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9B%B8%E7%99%96/</guid><description>&lt;p>鼯埋松果鴃懸屍，陋室徒藏百冊詩。 &lt;br>
開卷恐污長不讀，秦皇應笑我愚痴。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>葵涌工廈會友</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 19:09:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8B/</guid><description>&lt;p>取徑葵涌道，良朋相飲來。&lt;br>
人閒車馬靜，路黦綠苔開。&lt;br>
風送天雲遠，霞留暮色哀。&lt;br>
頹垣將拆盡，客別舊樓臺。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>悼從祖祖父</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%82%BC%E5%BE%9E%E7%A5%96%E7%A5%96%E7%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 21:57:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%82%BC%E5%BE%9E%E7%A5%96%E7%A5%96%E7%88%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p>清明未至立新冢，香火盈堂幡引魂。&lt;br>
冒雨梨花開遍野，迎風淚眼念先恩。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>冀嶺南景色依舊</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%86%80%E5%B6%BA%E5%8D%97%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E4%BE%9D%E8%88%8A/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 01:58:05 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%86%80%E5%B6%BA%E5%8D%97%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E4%BE%9D%E8%88%8A/</guid><description>&lt;p>樹倚東籬側，清池阡陌間。&lt;br>
萬田如一色，青嶂繞千鬟。&lt;br>
胡寇鐵馬盛，唐家薪火頑。&lt;br>
北風南嶺絕，不許渡韶關。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>春分始聞春雷</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%A5%E5%88%86%E5%A7%8B%E8%81%9E%E6%98%A5%E9%9B%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 17:26:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%A5%E5%88%86%E5%A7%8B%E8%81%9E%E6%98%A5%E9%9B%B7/</guid><description>&lt;p>今歲春雷晚，牆陰蘚早成。 &lt;br>
雲烏風驟起，一震百禽鳴。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>回鄉聞兒童皆不能語方言</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%9B%9E%E9%84%89%E8%81%9E%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%9E%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 21:30:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%9B%9E%E9%84%89%E8%81%9E%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%9E%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%80/</guid><description>&lt;p>塾盡異文授，童皆方語非。&lt;br>
隔山車馬鬧，鄰舍灶煙微。&lt;br>
子弟傳承懶，田間稼穡稀。&lt;br>
落花歸土去，不復護芳菲。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>